config GPIO_ADI_ADRV906X
	bool "Analog Devices Inc, ADRV906x SoC GPIO support"
	depends on PINCTRL_ADI_ADRV906X
	default PINCTRL_ADI_ADRV906X
	select GPIOLIB_IRQCHIP
	help
	  This option enables GPIO (General Purpose Input/Output) controller
	  support for Analog Devices ADRV906x System-on-Chip platforms. The
	  GPIO controller provides configurable I/O pins that can be used for
	  various digital signal operations including input sensing, output
	  control, and interrupt generation.

	  This driver also includes IRQ chip support for GPIO-based interrupts,
	  allowing GPIO pins to be used as interrupt sources.

	  Say Y here if you are building a kernel for ADRV906x hardware and
	  need GPIO functionality.
	  If unsure, say N.
